                        <li>Built scalable SaaS solutions for healthcare, retail, and travel industries</li>
                        <li>Designed business-critical applications that improved operational efficiency by 20% and reduced manual cost through automation</li>
                        <li>Accelerated product delivery for startup clients across multiple domains through reusable frontend and backend systems</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-fontPrimary/65">Technologies: React, React Native, Node.js, Next.js, MUI, SCSS, Redux, AWS, GCP, Firebase, MongoDB</p>
                </article>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-9">
