                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-fontPrimary/65">Technologies: RBAC, Tool Execution Controls, Input Validation, Prompt Diffing, Trace Inspection</p>
                </article>

                <article class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-fontPrimary/15">
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-fontPrimary">My Silent Thoughts</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-fontPrimary/50">Technical Blog</span>
                        <a href="https://sijosam.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs text-fontPrimary/50 hover:text-fontPrimary underline decoration-dashed ml-auto">Live ↗</a>
